# ManaTuner Pro - Environment Variables Example
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values

# ===========================================
# REQUIRED VARIABLES
# ===========================================

# None - ManaTuner Pro works in Privacy-First mode by default

# ===========================================
# OPTIONAL VARIABLES
# ===========================================

# Error Monitoring (optional - DISABLED in production by privacy decision)
# See CLAUDE.md "Sentry" section before re-enabling.
# VITE_SENTRY_DSN=https://your-sentry-dsn@sentry.io/project-id

# ===========================================
# NOTES
# ===========================================
# - All VITE_ prefixed variables are exposed to the client
# - Never commit actual values to git
# - Test the app without optional variables to ensure graceful degradation
# - For Vercel deployment, add these in Project Settings > Environment Variables
# - ManaTuner Pro works fully offline without any external dependencies
